==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Jiggish
<hw>Jig"gish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Resembling, or suitable for, a jig, or lively movement.</def>
<rj><au>Tatler.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Playful; frisky.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>She is never sad, and yet not <qex>jiggish</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Habington.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Jiggle</ent>⟦br⟧
